This Docker image is used to create a container in which to build an application
written in go (1.9.2) relying on glide for depency management.

In particular, we use it with circleci to automate building and testing. 
cf .cirleci/

Build the image - Update the version number if changes are made to the Dockerfile

```bash
docker build -t mosaicnetworks/glider:0.0.1 .
```

Push to Docker Hub:

```bash
docker login
docker push mosaicnetworks/glider:0.0.1
```
